  "title": "NCCN Guidelines\u00ae Insights: Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer, Version 7.2025.",
  "abstract": "The NCCN Guidelines for Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) provide recommendations for the treatment of NSCLC. These NCCN Guidelines Insights discuss recent updates to the NCCN Guidelines, with a focus on systemic therapy options for the treatment of patients with nonmetastatic NSCLC and the corresponding molecular testing considerations.",
